main event: Three cylindrical objects, approximately six feet in length, blue with white exhaust, were observed circling Chicago.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for about ten minutes, The observer was reportedly intoxicated at the time of the sighting, The objects were described as being cylindrical in shape, The sighting was part of Project Blue Book, The observer's opinion concurred with that of the Reporting Officer.
sighted object: three cylindrical objects in the sky
witness description: the observer was possibly intoxicated at the time of the sighting
